✅ Successfully installed OpenClaw and can run it normally
✅ Completed the creation of basic configuration files (`SOUL.md` / `USER.md` / `IDENTITY.md`)
✅ Understand the basic concepts of the memory system (`MEMORY.md` and `memorySearch`)
✅ Are familiar with the `workspace` directory structure
✅ Possess basic command-line operation skills

If the above conditions are not met, it is recommended to first read [https://x.com/onehopeA9/status/2025934420893708433](https://x.com/onehopeA9/status/2025934420893708433) (Link to basic tutorial)

