After completing this tutorial, your OpenClaw will achieve the following capability improvements:

| Module | Before | After |
|--------|--------|-------|
| Work Specifications | AI understands its role, but lacks process | Clear work flow, standardized memory writing |
| Memory System | Basic memory, but easy to forget | Multi-layer memory, automatic summarization, precise recall |
| Task Processing | Single-threaded serial execution | Multi-threaded parallel, team collaboration |
